          "provision_label_raw": "section",
          "text": "The DMS zone is located in the Downtown Periphery area surrounding much of the downtown core. The area supports many of the downtown's groundfloor commercial areas and pedestrian oriented streetscapes. The area supports a mix of commercial, office, small scale accommodations, and upper floor residential uses.",
